	<desc>This extremely sophisticated AI made for Queen Y herself can swap between multiple modes depending on the situation.
			
	Inherited Advanced Cognitive stats: is immune to fires and suffocation, immune to mind control and sees adjacent rooms, starts at level 2 skills.</desc>
	<cost>100</cost>
	<bp>2</bp>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
