<crewBlueprint name="fr_necromantic_cognitive">
	<title>Necromantic Cognitive</title>
	<short>Necro. Cognitive</short>
	<desc>An AI construct that has been twisted and corrupted by the Necro-Lich's powers. Any sentience it had before has been stripped away, leaving it only as a tool for her schemes.

	Inherited Advanced Cognitive stats: is immune to fires and suffocation, immune to mind control and sees adjacent rooms, starts at level 2 skills.</desc>
	<cost>100</cost>
	<bp>2</bp>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<powerList>
		<power>200 Max Health, quickly repairs itself out of combat.</power>
		<power>1.6x combat damage, moves at 1.6x speed. 1.6x repair speed</power>
		<power>Can be switched to its Beacon mode, being unable to move or act but also granting powerful bonuses to allied crew in the same ship as them.</power>
		<power>The crew is considered automated when in beacon mode.</power>
	</powerList>
</crewBlueprint>


