<crewBlueprint name="fr_unique_collector">
	<title>Nexus Collector</title>
	<short>Collector</short>
	<desc>A Sylvan who was responsible for the sudden appearance of strange new weapons to the multiverse.
	
	Inherited Sylvan stats: 250 HP, 1.5x combat damage, massive hazardous damage resistance, telepathic powers, mind control immunity</desc>
	<cost>250</cost>
	<bp>2</bp>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<powerList>
		<power>Active Ability: Deploys a Spider Bomb that unleashes 3 friendly uncontrollable hatchling spiders that live for 10 seconds.</power>
		<power>Portable shield generator makes allies in the same room as him take 20% less damage and deal 5% more damage.</power>
		<power>Portable battery provides 2 power to occupied systems. 2.5x extinguishing speed.</power>
	</powerList>
</crewBlueprint>

<crewBlueprint name="fr_unique_cylvan">
	<title>Nexus Deserter</title>
	<short>Deserter</short>
	<desc>A Sylvan who abandoned his job and past life to live with the supposedly extinct Commonwealths.
	
	Inherited Sylvan stats: 250 HP, massive hazardous damage resistance, telepathic powers, mind control immunity
	Inherited Commonwealth stats: Cannot fight, 3x repair speed</desc>
	<cost>250</cost>
	<bp>2</bp>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<powerList>
		<power>Active Ability: (1 charge) Deploys a stun Bomb that can stun crew for 999 seconds and deals 10 ion damage.</power>
		<power>Moves at 1.5x speed. Sabotages at 2x speed.</power>
		<power>Immune to stuns.</power>
	</powerList>
</crewBlueprint>

<crewBlueprint name="fr_spherax">
	<title>Spherax</title>
	<short>Spherax</short>
	<desc>One of the last remaining members of the race known as the "Spherax", timeless beings solely focused on bettering themselves and pursuing their goals doggedly.</desc>
	<cost>150</cost>
	<bp>2</bp>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<powerList>
		<power>Active Ability: Can speed up or slow down the room they are currently in for 5 seconds.</power>
		<power>200 health, immune to hazards.</power>
		<power>Can teleport between rooms and ships. Sabotages at 3x speed.</power>
		<power>Instantly regenerates health after being outside of combat for 10 seconds.</power>
		<power>Can only shoot. Shoots very slowly but deals 5x damage.</power>
	</powerList>
</crewBlueprint>

<crewBlueprint name="fr_unique_billvan">
	<title>Hektar Exile</title>
	<short>Exile</short>
	<desc>After witnessing the death of his brother at the hands of the Rebels, this Billy decided to take up his brother's mantle, even discovering the Nexus and convincing Sylvan Prime to accept him.
	
	Inherited Sylvan stats: 1.5x combat damage, telepathic powers, mind control immunity, starts with level 2 on all skills, doesn't lose skills when cloned</desc>
	<cost>250</cost>
	<bp>2</bp>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<powerList>
		<power>Active Ability: Can enter and exit his box at any time. While inside the box he will be fully immune to hazards.</power>
		<power>Active Ability: Deploys a Breach, Lockdown, and Fire Bomb at the same time.</power>
		<power>Heals at half speed from passive sources, but regenerates 20 hp/s while in the box.</power>
		<power>Max Health is increased to 150.</power>
	</powerList>
</crewBlueprint>

