<crewBlueprint name="fr_unique_vance_one">
	<title>Legion Admiral</title>
	<short>Admiral</short>
	<desc>The Vance of Universe 1, leader of the Legionnaires and the usurper of the Rebel leadership. Very much not a good guy.
	
	Inherited Legionnaire Operative stats: movement speed is doubled, trained in lvl 2 skills, greatly resistant to O2 and fire hazards.</desc>
	<cost>250</cost>
	<bp>2</bp>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
