		<power>Fully drains power while in the same room as non-essential enemy systems. Drains 2 power out of essential systems.</power>
		<power>Constantly regenerates 5 hp/s. Deals 0.4x damage in combat.</power>
	</powerList>
</crewBlueprint>

<crewBlueprint name="fr_reformed_searak">
	<desc>One of the oldest Duskbringers, driven mad by a sabotaged clone bay. Now, he searches only for redemption and peace.
	
