<weaponBlueprint name="FR_WITHER_PROTOTYPE_PACIFIER">
	<type>BOMB</type>
	<flavorType>Aether Projector</flavorType>
	<tip>tip_scanner</tip>
	<title>'Silencer'</title>
	<short>'Silencer'</short>
	<desc>This bizarre weapon creates a self-controlled holographic projection. Although it can't man systems, repair, sabotage, or heal through normal means, it is highly durable and will doggedly pursue enemies.
		
	The hologram will decay if present on your ship.</desc>
	<tooltip>Spawns a highly uncontrollable and highly durable wither hologram that will fight for you until the end of the encounter. Deals 1 system damage and always breaches the room chosen.</tooltip>
