<weaponBlueprint name="FR_AUGUSTUS_MISSILE">
	<type>BURST</type>
	<flavorType>Scrap Converter</flavorType>
	<drone_targetable>1</drone_targetable>
	<tip>tip_missiles_burst</tip>
	<title>'Midas' Burst Missiles</title>
	<short>'Midas'</short>
	<desc>Burst Missiles fire multiple low damage warheads for the price of one through patented replication technology.</desc>
	<descriptionOverride>A gun made out of pure gold and ectoplasm. Fires a set of 3 golden warheads which all have different properties at the cost of needing both scrap and a missile to fire.

		Stats:
		Required Power: 2
		Charge Time: 15 seconds
		Scrap Consumption: 3
		Missile Consumption: 1

		Shot Radius: 35
		Fires 3 Random Missiles Per Shot
		
		Red Missile: 1 hull and 3 system damage, 100% fire chance, fully ignites the room hit.
		Blue Missile: 2 hull damage, hullbust, 100% breach chance, slowly erode the system in the targeted room.
		Green Missile: 1 hull and 2 Ion Damage, stuns crew hit for 10 seconds, destroys any crew drone hit instantly.
		Cyan Missile: 1 Damage, undetectable by certain Defense Drones, locks down room, inflicts Cryo-Sentry debuffs on all crew members in room for the lockdown duration.
		Purple Missile: 1 system and 90 crew damage, inflicts radiation debuffs, inflicts 3 damage per second over 25 seconds, can't miss, deals 1 system damage to surrounding rooms.
		
		Default Price: 250~   -   Selling Price: 125~
	</descriptionOverride>
	<tooltipOverride>Required Power: 2
		Charge Time: 15 seconds
		Scrap Consumption: 3
		Missile Consumption: 1

		Shot Radius: 35
		Fires 3 Random Missiles Per Shot
		
