		Cyan Missile: 1 Damage, undetectable by certain Defense Drones, locks down room, inflicts Cryo-Sentry debuffs on all crew members in room for the lockdown duration.
		Purple Missile: 1 system and 90 crew damage, inflicts radiation debuffs, inflicts 3 damage per second over 25 seconds, can't miss, deals 1 system damage to surrounding rooms.</tooltipOverride>
	<tooltip>Fires a blast of debris across a random area doing up to 3 damage.</tooltip>
