	<title>G's Magical Shield</title>
	<desc>An absurdly powerful energy shield unit. Has an integrity of no less than 80 points, and offers the ability to jam an enemy's bypass unit before battle if they have one.</desc>
	<cost>450</cost>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
