<augBlueprint name="FR_PSIONIC_HELMETS">
	<title>Psionic Helmets</title>
	<desc>The crew in this ship are equipped with unique helmets made by the Watcher themselves, giving them a taste of a siren's psionic prowess.

As long as any enemy crew is mind controlled, your non-Siren crew drain enemy crew in the same room as them for 5hp/s. Also prevents non-Rhyme enemy crew from teleporting.</desc>
