<augBlueprint name="FR_FORBIDDEN_DESIGN">
	<title>Forbidden Design</title>
	<desc>This ship is constructed with horrific eldritch technology lining the halls. It emits waves of shaped chaotic energy that inflict Blasphemy, causing all enemy crew and drones to lose their death effects.
				
The technology also functions as an energy shield with an integrity of 12 hit points, and creates random bonuses that occur when the ship takes hull damage.</desc>
