</augBlueprint>
<augBlueprint name="FR_LAB_SPECTER_FLAWLESS_ASCENSION">
	<title>Flawless Ascension</title>
	<desc>Your Specters take twice as long to charge their abilities but their abilities become boosted in unique ways.
		Slimer: 
		- DEVOUR: Removes the system damage and allows it to be used in the enemy ship.
		- EAT: Now deals 75 damage to enemy crew and heals Slimer for 35 for each enemy crew in the room.
		Phys: Ion damage is raised to 8 and the stun now only affects enemies.
		Aleenor: Raises crew damage to 100 damage and system damage to 4 damage.
		Vin:
		- BOOST: Removes the self damage.
		- FUSION: Vin's fire healing will be doubled for 10 seconds after activating the ability.
		Cleo: The drones also gain double damage for the duration.
		Zulu: Removes the movement speed, sabotage and damage penalties during the effect.
		G: Also spawns 3 undead specters for the duration.
		Frostwall: Removes the self damage and causes frozen crew to take full damage for the duration.
		Deathbloom: Dobules the duration of the spores and lowers enemy's speed while affected by the spores by 10%.
		Pok: Their morph ability's cooldown is cut to 10 seconds in all forms.
		Charror: Their ability now affects all crew types and only applies to enemies.
		Leo: The increased damage taken now applies to enemies in the room instead.
		Searak: Removes the post explosion stun.
		Augustus: Now only costs 1 scrap to fully heal him.
		Sally: The hatchling and adult abilities now only have a 1 second cooldown, while the weaver form ability's affects all ships.
		Prince: Breaches and starts a fire in the room as well.
		Tririac: Tririac becomes immune to stun during the effect.
	</desc>
	<cost>0</cost>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<stackable>true</stackable>
</augBlueprint>
<augBlueprint name="FR_LAB_SPECTER_TAILORED_SPECIALIZATION">
	<title>Tailored Specialization</title>
	<desc>Your Specters' strengths and well as their weaknesses are vastly improved.
		Slimer: Reduces his active ability cooldowns by 50% - Halves his crew damage.
		Phys: Provides double her base power - Can't sabotage.
		Aleenor: Doubles her damage - Can't repair.
		Vin: Doubles his health - Halves his speed.
		Cleo: Gains a 1.3x bonus to health, speed, repair and damage - Cannot fight enemy drones directly. 
		Zulu: Doubles his sabotage damage - Halves his crew damage.
		G: Doubles the healing gained from hazards - Raises her active ability cooldowns by 50%.
		Frostwall: Doubles his ranged damage - Halves his hp.
		Deathbloom: Sets her o2 production to 2.0 (old was 0.1) - Halves her heal speed. 
		Pok: They move 50% faster and reduces their active ability cooldowns by 50% - They use 2 crew slots.
		Charror: Doubles their repair speed - Halves their crew damage.
		Leo: Doubles their power drain - Doubles their stun time.
		Searak: Halves his damage taken - Halves his sabotage damage.
		Augustus: Adds a 1.2x multipler to his sabotage, damage and health - Halves his movement speed.
		Sally: Constantly heals for 15 hp/s - Halves health.
		Prince: Doubles movement speed - Halves repair speed.
		Tririac: Doubles the damage mind controled crew do in the same room as them - They are stunned 10 times longer.
	</desc>
	<cost>0</cost>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<stackable>true</stackable>
</augBlueprint>
<augBlueprint name="FR_LAB_SPECTER_SPECTRAL_EXISTENCE">
	<title>Spectral Existence</title>
	<desc>Specters don't use up any crew slots. Generic Specters will be prioritized first in crew loss events above *any* other crew.</desc>
	<cost>0</cost>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<stackable>true</stackable>
