<augBlueprint name="FR_HEKTAR_SUPERSHIELD_BASE">
	<title>Hektar Modular Shield</title>
	<desc>A powerful energy shield created by the one and only Billvan. It has an integrity of 10 hitpoints, and can be modified with any Hektar module to apply a powerful secondary effect.
	Module Effects:
	Cooldown: Boosts shield recharge rate by 200%.
	Anti-Bio: Makes your ship an Auto-ship while slotted.
	Stun: Your crew become immune to stun. Enemies are stunned for triple the normal duration, and they will be stunned automatically every 5 seconds while in your ship.
	Pierce: Enemy weapons and drones pierce 7 fewer shield layers.
	Hullbuster: Provides a 50% chance to negate incoming hull damage.
	Lockdown: Your non-beam weapons apply lockdown. All of your weapons pierce an additional shield layer.
	Fire: Your systems and crew don't take fire damage.
	Accuracy: Your weapons have 30% more accuracy.
	Power: The energy shield's integrity is increased to 20 layers, but your normal shields will have their recharge rate reduced by 50%.</desc>
	<cost>150</cost>
	<bp>15</bp>
	<rarity>0</rarity>
	<stackable>false</stackable>
</augBlueprint>

